IT’S that time of the year when hearts get broken. This is because some boyfriends disappear during the festive season. Some people even call it boyfriend leave. Ntombfuthi Magwaza (30) shared on Twitter that she knew how this felt as her boyfriend dumped her on 30 November last year. “Ladies, just prepare yourselves. Men want to spend their bonuses peacefully with slay queens. At the end they will come back to us when they are broke in January,” she said. SunReaders also shared their experiences about the boyfriend leave. Sex and relationship expert Dr Eve told Daily Sun she was aware of festive season break ups. She said the festive season could be a ticking time bomb for unstable relationships.